Remuneration of the members of the Managing Board

Members of the Managing Board received cash compensation of €18.8 million. The fair value of share-based compensation amounted to €10.5 million for 170,111 stock awards. The Company granted contributions under the BSAV to members of the Managing Board totaling €2.2 million.

Therefore, the compensation and benefits attributable to members of the Managing Board amounted to €31.6 million in total.